lockerproject: connects to web data services and pulls it all together
telehash: distributed connection discovery
singly: secure hosting for lockers

locker will get all your data.  woo.  then, you can share it with
people over any service you write an app for, but in particular, you
can just be a telehash node with it and verify rsa keys of incoming
connections (are they really your friends?) and then replace diaspora.

action: 
 - write connectors to your favorite data
 - write apps to do interesting things with your data
